  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"the-problem\">The Problem</h2>\n<p class=\"\">The first thing most people do when they wake up is grab their phone and doom-scroll. News apps are designed to maximize engagement, not inform. Social feeds are designed to maximize time-on-platform, not satisfaction. I wanted something different.</p>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"what-im-building\">What I'm Building</h2>\n<p class=\"\">MorningRadio—an iOS app designed to be a healthy \"first screen.\" Quick news summaries, curated links from my Pinboard bookmarks, and audio briefings. The TikTok-style vertical swipe interaction, but filled with things that actually make your morning better.</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1200/v1755098720/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.25.04_AM.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 80vw, 100vw\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>\n<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"\">Design principles:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc\">\n<li class=\"\">Finite content—you can reach the end</li>\n<li class=\"\">Audio-first for eyes-free consumption</li>\n<li class=\"\">Curated sources, not algorithmic feeds</li>\n<li class=\"\">Satisfying, not addicting</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"\" id=\"current-state\">Current State</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Active development. Experimenting with home screen widgets (harder than expected on iOS) and audio synthesis for spoken briefings.</p>\n<p class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_400/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 400w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_800/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 800w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1200/v1749668160/Screenshot_2025-06-11_at_2.55.49_PM.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 768px) 80vw, 100vw\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></p>",
